main event: Corporal xxxxxxx reported observing a bright, fluorescent light moving rapidly across the sky in Hawaii on June 30, 1955.
interesting points: The light was described as approximately 30 to 40 feet in diameter and at an altitude of 200 to 300 feet,The light emitted no engine noise and left no visible tail,The light traveled about 2000 yards before disappearing,Corporal xxxxxxx is deemed a reliable witness,There were multiple sightings of unidentified aerial objects in Hawaii around the same timeframe.
sighted object: fluorescent light moving across the sky
